      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "曹彬引赵匡胤同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00002",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹彬"
      ],
      "text": "打开玉笼飞彩凤，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00003",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "蹬断金锁走蛟龙。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00004",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹彬"
      ],
      "text": "请。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00005",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "院子迎上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00006",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟请。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00007",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹彬"
      ],
      "text": "兄长请坐。家院，准备酒饭伺候。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00008",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "院子"
      ],
      "text": "是。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00009",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "院子摆酒。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00010",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "院子"
      ],
      "text": "酒饭到。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00011",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹彬"
      ],
      "text": "兄长请酒。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00012",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "院子下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00013",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟，时才在关前，被崔浩那厮，差人捉拿于我。若非嫂嫂张氏，叫我一声丈夫，愚兄险遭不测。",
      "text_length": 43
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00014",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹彬"
      ],
      "text": "此乃是仁兄洪福，有道是吉人自有天相也。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00015",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟呀！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00016",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "顶板原板",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "说什么吉人有天佑，细听我赵玄郎诉说根由：恨只恨崔浩贼要下毒手，他与我一定要做下对头。他命人在四门紧紧把守，要害我赵玄郎他方罢休。幸遇着张氏嫂嫂将我打救，因此上逃性命才得回头。",
      "text_length": 87
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00017",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹彬"
      ],
      "text": "兄长不必泪双流，小弟言来听从头：得饮酒来且饮酒，待等明日做良谋。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00018",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "曹彬睡。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00019",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "听一言来心内忧，倒叫某家皱眉头。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00020",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "起更鼓。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00021",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟！睡熟了。咳！想我赵玄郎半生落魄，屡遭凶险，不知何日才是我出头之日！思想起来，好不烦闷人也！",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00022",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "赵玄郎坐书房心中纳闷，二相公心无事瞌睡沉沉。无奈何推纱窗强把心散，真乃是中秋月，星星朗朗，朗朗星星，月到中秋，万里无云分外的光明。",
      "text_length": 65
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00023",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "走金桥曾遇着先生苗训，那先生排八卦会算子平。俺玄郎将八字从头推算，他算我到后来有九五之尊。周文王全凭着三兄四弟，俺玄郎也要仗四海宾朋。且喜得今日里逃了性命，跳龙潭出虎穴脱了残生。恨不得挺长枪刺落玉兔，用金钩钩出了红日东升。",
      "text_length": 111
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00024",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张氏上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00025",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "谯楼上打罢二更尽，走到堂前看分明。悄悄儿来在窗门外，暗地里听他说原因。",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00026",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "奴家张氏。时才关前遇一红脸大汉，颇似我家丈夫。是我向前叫了他一声，被官军将奴赶去。既然是我丈夫归来，为何不见到来？方才邻舍陈家伯伯言到，有一红脸大汉，在二相公书房安歇。是奴家暗自出房，来在此地，听他说些什么。",
      "text_length": 104
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00027",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "且住！想我赵匡胤，今日在关前，被官军盘问。若非被张氏嫂嫂叫了我一声丈夫，我命休矣。看将起来，真真的难得呀难得！哎咦，什么难得？此人乃是旁人的妻子，倘若是我的妻子，既然叫人一声丈夫，我便一刀将她杀死！",
      "text_length": 99
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00028",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张氏倒跌，急跑下。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00029",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "张氏生来太奇情，错把旁人叫夫君。我前思后想心烦闷，又听得谯楼上打三更。",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00030",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "华佗上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00031",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "华佗"
      ],
      "text": "在洞中奉了玉帝令，割除肉瘤救真龙。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00032",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华佗"
      ],
      "text": "吾乃华佗是也。只因大宋天子赵匡胤身生肉瘤。崔浩命人，各处严拿与他。吾今奉了上帝敕旨，前去为他割除肉瘤，以救危难。就此走走。",
      "text_length": 61
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00033",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "华佗"
      ],
      "text": "天下纷纷刀兵乱，无人执掌锦江山。大宋真龙身遭难，去到曹府走一番。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00034",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华佗"
      ],
      "text": "来此已是。看他熟睡，待我与他医治起来。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00035",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖牌子〗。华佗用刀割瘤，敷药。赵匡胤看。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00036",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "你是何人？莫非前来行刺么？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00037",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华佗"
      ],
      "text": "非也。贫道乃是汉室华佗。今日特来，为主公割除肉瘤，以救危难。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00038",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "原来是华先生到了，多蒙医治，感恩非浅！",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00039",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华佗"
      ],
      "text": "臣前来讨封。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00040",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "封你为药圣真人。去往华山归位去吧。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00041",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "华佗"
      ],
      "text": "谢主龙恩。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00042",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "华佗"
      ],
      "text": "三呼万岁谢皇恩，去到华山且修真。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00043",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "华佗下。张氏魂上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00044",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "飘飘荡荡风一阵，来了张氏一鬼魂。将身且把书房进，万岁台前诉详情。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00045",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "下跪何人？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00046",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "张氏鬼魂。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00047",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "前来做甚？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00048",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "前来讨封。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00049",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "多蒙你救驾之恩，理应封赠。你且听了。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00050",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "玄郎开言加封赠，张氏嫂嫂听详情：关前蒙你救我命，理当加封受隆恩。华山老母加封你，安受香烟称正神。",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00051",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "谢主隆恩。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00052",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "谢过皇恩忙站定，去到华山为正神。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00053",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张氏下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00054",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄导板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹彬"
      ],
      "text": "时才间朦胧方睡醒，",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00055",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "曹彬看。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00056",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹彬"
      ],
      "text": "呀！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00057",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹彬"
      ],
      "text": "又只见红日自东升。迈步且出书房门，去到后堂看分明。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00058",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "曹彬下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00059",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄导板",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "昨夜晚三更得一梦，",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00060",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "华佗技艺果然精。我这里急忙来观定，",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00061",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "赵匡胤看。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00062",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "肉瘤不见喜吟吟。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00063",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "昨夜三更时分偶得一梦，梦见华佗前来，将我的肉瘤割掉。肉瘤已去，我今日定可出关也！",
      "text_length": 40
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00064",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "人言华佗艺道精，话不虚传果然真。今日去到关前论。看崔浩把我怎样行？",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00065",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "曹彬上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00066",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹彬"
      ],
      "text": "时才家院报一信，张氏嫂嫂命归阴。将身且把书房进，尊声兄长听分明。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00067",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹彬"
      ],
      "text": "启禀兄长：我那张氏嫂嫂昨夜三更十分悬梁自尽了。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00068",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "不好了！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00069",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "听罢言来吃一惊，张氏为我丧残生。但愿得灵魂儿早归仙境，我纵死黄泉也感你的大恩。",
      "text_length": 39
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00070",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟，愚兄想得一计，可以逃出虎口。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00071",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 71,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹彬"
      ],
      "text": "兄长有何妙计？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00072",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 72,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "烦劳贤弟将愚兄捆绑起来，上了枷锁，去到衙前投首。但不知贤弟意下如何？",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00073",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 73,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹彬"
      ],
      "text": "兄长说哪里话来！想那崔浩与兄长夙有冤仇，今日他命人四下查访捉拿兄长。今日兄长不去逃生，反去送死。此事断断使不得！",
      "text_length": 56
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00074",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 74,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟有所不知。想那崔浩，虽然与我有仇，但是他并未见过我面，只知愚兄身有肉瘤。今日愚兄肉瘤已去，纵然见我，他又岂奈我何？",
      "text_length": 59
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00075",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 75,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹彬"
      ],
      "text": "话虽如此，还要兄长三思，免得后悔。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00076",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 76,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟不必多虑，愚兄自有言语回答于他。我有一言，贤弟听了！",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00077",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 77,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮二六板",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "手挽手儿把话论，尊一声贤弟听分明：曾记得当年在原郡，幼习武艺共刀兵。也是我家道甚贫困，浪荡江湖四海飘零。弟兄们结拜在飞龙岭，好似一母同胞生。恨崔浩与我有仇恨，苦苦要害我命残生。昨日关前幸逃命，多亏张氏救我的恩。烦贤弟你且将我捆，去到关前通姓名。谅他不识我赵匡胤，改名换姓诈他们。今日我肉瘤无踪影，他定放我去逃生。倘若一朝得侥幸，统领兵马杀仇人。若将崔浩来拿定，千刀万剐不留情。贤弟休得多议论，你且大胆放宽心。来来来，将枷锁与我齐上捆，",
      "text_length": 217
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00078",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 78,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "赵匡胤带枷锁。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00079",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 79,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "去到衙前把话论。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00080",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 80,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹彬"
      ],
      "text": "玄郎果是英雄汉，足智多谋胆包天。二人一同去冒险，哪怕虎穴与龙潭。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00081",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 81,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "叫贤弟与我把路带，大胆前去走一番！",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01028007_e00082",
      "play_id": "01028007",
      "scene_id": "01028007_s01",
